      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PAW ENNA (2) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing fourth (22.51) in a Grade 5 at Ballarat. Form here sound including two wins. Better than last start and worth following up. SERENITY GIRL (3) was prominent throughout but too strong in the run home to score by 1.3 lengths (22.43) at Ballarat in Grade 5. Has failed to finish in the placings from six starts here. Can continue on with her winning form. BIG MAKO (1) was in the money two back in a Grade 5 at this track then jumped from a squeeze draw last time and was not far away when third (23.00) over 400m at this track. Well placed here and should do much better. SICILY (7) will have admirers again after placing at this track and distance last time out.",
